div.p:
“Divine being, these are the four feet of bodhisattvas: the foot of the Dharma, the foot of purpose, the foot of
                        engaging in the ascetic practices and having few possessions, and the foot of gathering Lhasa: tshogs gsog pa’i rkang pa;
                            Degé, Stok: tshogs sogs pa’i rkang pa; Choné: tshogs sog pa’i rkang pa. the accumulations of the path of awakening.
